tip.text: Staff was very friendly. Cheesecake and Carrot Cake is really good.
Salmon & Eggs are to die for. If you love salmon of course 😅
Had a Turkey Brie sandwich. It was good and go along with a cup of chai latte, it was a little sweet but still it was not bad.
"Everything on everything" bagel is awesome. Very limited seating but come early in the day and you will be fine.
The Pedestrian (croissant) is very popular here and it is indeed tasty and go along with a cup of coffee, perfect.
I'm going with the recommended drink "chai latte". It was indeed good, not so sweet. Visited around 4pm and it gets abit crowded.
